{"word":"H7429 - רָמַס - râmaç - raw-mas' - Oppressor","slug":"H7429","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָמַס</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râmaç"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-mas'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Oppressor"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05DE;&#x05E1; - ra&#x0302;mas</b> - <i>raw-mas'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>tread</i> upon (as a potter, in walking or abusively): - oppressor, stamp upon, trample (under feet), tread (down, upon)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4823\">H4823</a>"}]}